section.section:
In addition to any other penalty allowed by law, a court may declare the defendant ineligible to operate a motor vehicle for the period of time that any amount of restitution ordered under this section remains unpaid, where the restitution is imposed as the result of the commission of the following offenses:
KRS 434.650;
KRS 434.655;
KRS 434.660;
KRS 434.670;
KRS 434.690;
KRS 514.030;
KRS 514.040;
KRS 514.050;
KRS 514.060;
KRS 514.070;
KRS 514.080;
KRS 514.090;
KRS 514.110;
KRS 514.120; or
KRS 506.120.
